[l] Die Machtuebernahme Hitlers gelang dank Austerity. Denn Austerity betraf die Mittelschicht.With dashed hopes and a loss of faith in the Weimar Republic, fury and despair were channelled into the ranks of populists and demagogues, with the Nazi party campaigning against austerity and offering promises for a new era of prosperity. The lowest status groups and the unemployed turned to the Communists, but those just above in the economic hierarchy, who had more to lose from the tax hikes intended to enhance central government finances, favoured the Nazis.Na, kommt das jemandem bekannt vor?
